# Words to be kept as single units (not split by NVASR tokenizer).
# Self-referential format: word word (same as NVV entries in mfa_ipa.dict).
# The tokenizer's phonetic approximations (pinyin fragments, single
# letters) at the word's position will be merged into the canonical form.
#
# Add new words below — one per line:
# ria ria
# call call
ria ria
call call
